    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride and it's looking for a new adventure! This car has been so good to me\u2014it's super reliable, runs smoothly, and has been well-maintained over the years. It\u2019s in really solid shape and is ready to hit the road with its next owner. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
