    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of well-maintained engineering, offering a driving experience that remains tight and responsive. The exterior finish holds a beautiful luster, showing only the light, expected character marks of a car that has been driven and loved. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs with a smooth, rhythmic idle, backed by a comprehensive service history that ensures peace of mind. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the premium seating is firm and supportive, and the dashboard remains free of cracks or fading. Every feature, from the crisp audio system to the ice-cold dual-zone climate control, operates flawlessly. This car isn't just a mode of transport; it\u2019s a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has many miles of adventure left to offer. It has been garaged and regularly detailed, ensuring it still turns heads on the road.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
