    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me through every trip. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great and feels smooth on the road, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 31500.0,
