      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal power distribution. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate structural fatigue, and the rod bearings have been serviced as preventative maintenance. The suspension is dialed in with upgraded bushings and dampened by a refreshed OEM-plus setup, ensuring the chassis remains composed under high lateral loads. A mechanically robust specimen with a clean rev-range and precise shift gates.",
